II. Description:

A script that can be used to automate the building of
yocto images for Intel Galileo.

The image built is 1.0.1. Older images are not supported

More information about the manual build process can be found here
https://communities.intel.com/community/makers/documentation/galileodocuments

To use this script
Download it and make sure it is executable

Type 
./build_clanton.sh to run it with default settings
                     OR
Type ./build_clanton.sh --help for more advanced usage instructions.

This has been tested on Debian 7.5 and may not work on other
systems.

The default work directory is ~/build and the process requires an
internet connection.

Estimated time is from 0-10 hours with the avg. being 4.

Please email bug reports to the authors.

